text: The Eastern Gulf Fleet Command () or officially Eastern Fleet (EF), is one of the regional fleets of the Saudi Arabian Navy. It is headquartered and Royal Naval Base at Jubail, on the east coast of the Arabian Kingdom, responsible for military operations of the Saudi Navy in the Gulf waters. ==See also== *Western Fleet (Saudi Arabia) ==References== ==External links== * Fleet Category:Naval warfare Category:Naval fleets Category:Military units and formations established in 1795 Category:Military units and formations of Saudi Arabia
title: Eastern Fleet (Saudi Arabia)
